Now, we solve the value of d2 using the equation in Step 3: 

&nbsp;

$$\begin{aligned}
\textbf{d}_{2}&=0.21-0.20\times\sqrt{0.50}\\[15pt]
&=0.21-0.20\times0.71\\[15pt]
&=0.21-0.142\\[15pt]
&=0.068\space\text{or}\space0.07\space\text{when rounded}
\end{aligned}$$

Thus, the value of d2 is 0.07.
